headline: Tractor Supply’s Spring Crop of 4-H Paper Clovers Has Arrived
summary: BRENTWOOD, Tenn., April 17, 2025--Tractor Supply Company (NASDAQ: TSCO), the largest rural lifestyle retailer in the United States, is ready to kick off its spring Paper Clover fundraiser, a biannual event that has generated millions of dollars in scholarships for 4-H youth. From April 18 through May 5, customers can purchase a paper clover at checkout in Tractor Supply stores nationwide or online at TractorSupply.com.
